HEADWORD: Dancer
<hw>Dan"cer</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who dances or who
practices dancing.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>The merry dancers</b></col>, <cd>beams of the northern
lights when they rise and fall alternately without any considerable
change of length. See <cref>Aurora borealis</cref>, under
<er>Aurora</er>.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Danceress</ent>⟦br⟧
